Documents.Title: Computers and Social Controversy
Documents.Description: Liike the Industrial Revolution, the computer revolution, in the main, is regarded as a positive benefit. And yet, when specific individuals are personally affected by the encroachment of computers, they do not always view their particular situations with bubbling good humor. Most especially, whenever the computer intrudes on their privacy, threatens their job security, or usurps their position as the earth's preeminent creatures, raging controversies inevitably result.
